nodes.text: This assassin probe was in service of the Death Watch and the Confederacy of Independent Systems during the second year of the Clone Wars.

In 21 BBY, during the Clone Wars this assassin probe was smuggled by Tal Merrik onboard the ship Coronet with two others, to assassinate Duchess Satine Kryze during her voyage to Coruscant. Jedi General Anakin Skywalker and his unit of clone troopers defeated this one first out of the other two.
